5
One Move Captures White (1)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par When it is merely a life and death problem it is very easy. However, in a real game, a lot of mistakes are made in this position.
\par
\par One move determines everything. Of course, there's only one move to capture white.
\par }
